    <title>Amendments to the new firefighters' pension scheme 2006: automatic enrolment</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This consultation covers amendments to the new firefighters’ pension scheme, as set out in the &lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2006/3432/made"&gt;Firefighters’ Pension Scheme (England) Order 2006&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is so that fire and rescue authorities can comply with their duties for automatic enrolment under workplace pension reform.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We received 13 responses to the consultation and summary of responses is available above.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
